@{bg fill}                                @{fg shine}Introduction@{fg text}                                 @{bg back}


          Have you ever been stuck in one of those corridors in
          AlienBreed 3 - Tower Assault?

          This is the solutions to all your problems and wonderings.
          Now you will be able to see what's after that corridor or very
          difficult sector.

          This program offers you the ultimate help to AlienBreed 3.
          With a very easy-to-use GUI you can choose where to go and which
          weapons you would like to have. There's no problem getting a lot
          of credits either.

          If you'd like some help on your holy quest killing aliens, then
          this is the tool for you.
          If you, on the other hand, only wants to kick ass, then this is
          also the tool for you.

          Have much fun.   Happy Hunting!


          @{" Requirements " link "Req" 0}

