@{fg shine}@{bg fill}                                    Info@{fg text}                                     @{bg back}


          AB3-LCG was programmed by @{" me " link "Me" 0} in September 1996.

          I used AmosPro 2.0 utilising Pietro Ghizzoni's GUI-extension
          and the GUI-patched version of AmosPro-Compiler.

          I got the idee when I got hold of Stefan Greifenberg's text
          about the AB3 levelcode. His work is very good, but is now
          obsolete. I have cracked the code into the smallest fragments
          so it would be easy to use in a program.  But it's still
          thanks to him I was able to make this.


